  <brief_title>Quality Assurance of Cognitive-behavioral Therapy</brief_title>
  <official_title>Quality Assurance of Cognitive-behavioral Therapy: Adherence and Competence in Therapists and Treatment Outcome in Patients With Depression and Anxiety</official_title>
